VB22-027: Fix potential leak when resolution fails early in backjumping routine.

The backjumping clause that we set up was not free'd in the early return path
of the Backjump routine.

Also, rename some of the test case files to simplify further copies.
VB22-027: Avoid leaking when theory check raises an exception.
VB22-027: Avoid memory leak when resolution fails early.

Testsuite: add a mode to run tests under Valgrind

TN: W112-021
Address comment from Raph's review.
Add -flto flag to prod builds.

VB22-027: Mention python instead of python3 in testsuite runner.

Python3 cannot be found on Windows test machines which causes AdaSAT testing
to fail immediately.

VB22-027: Quote paths given to relocate-build-tree.

Non quoted paths turned backslashes to nothing and made gprbuild fail on
windows due to looking for nonsensical paths.
